Usage: deleteRoutingHalo [-help] [-lithoHalo] {-allBlocks  | -block <name> | -cell <name> | -inst <name> | -designHalo }

-help           # Prints out the command usage
-allBlocks      # for all blocks (bool, required)
-block <name>   # block names (list, required)
-cell <name>    # cell names (list, required)
-designHalo     # for all partitions (bool, required)
-inst <name>    # instance names (list, required)
-lithoHalo      # for litho halo (bool, optional)